sc_cat_item.description: When requesting this service you will be prompted for the name of the service as the internal consumer would see it, a directory structure for where it would be presented on the internal service portal, and the starting variables.  From there a new case will be created in development, and an email will be sent to you. The email will contain a link to edit the case and a link to view the case in the portal.
